<sect1 id="dir_332ee2fb83ffca0bb7838dea50093abe_1autotoc_md137">
<title>helios::engine::ecs::systems</title><para>Core ECS systems for entity management and hierarchy propagation.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_332ee2fb83ffca0bb7838dea50093abe_1autotoc_md138">
<title>Overview</title><para>This submodule contains systems that operate on fundamental ECS components. These systems are typically registered early in the game loop to ensure proper entity state before game-specific systems run.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_332ee2fb83ffca0bb7838dea50093abe_1autotoc_md139">
<title>Systems</title><para><table rows="2" cols="2"><row>
